Norma Connolly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Norma_Connolly 0 Norma Connolly (August 27, 1927 – November 18, 1998) was an American actress having a career spanning five decades and known for her roles on The Young Marrieds as Lena Karr Gilroy and General Hospital as Ruby Anderson.
